that, despite her past mistakes,

80
00:03:34,388 --> 00:03:37,954
Frost now only wishes
to serve this city,

81
00:03:37,956 --> 00:03:41,515
alongside our greatest
protector, the Flash.

82
00:03:41,518 --> 00:03:43,083
Still,

83
