84
00:03:45,373 --> 00:03:48,852
Which is why she's
seeking a fair punishment.

85
00:03:48,854 --> 00:03:51,325
Not only because it's
the right thing to do,

86
00:03:51,328 --> 00:03:54,467
but to prove once and for all

87
00:03:54,469 --> 00:03:57,165
who she really is.

88
00:03:57,167 --> 00:03:59,167
She's a flawed person

89
00:03:59,169 --> 00:04:00,995
who has changed her ways

90
00:04:00,997 --> 00:04:04,477
and become a hero, in her own right.

91
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,479
Well-argued, Ms. Horton.

92
00:04:06,481 --> 00:04:07,656
Counselor Strong,

93
00:04:07,659 --> 00:04:10,313
would the State like to
make an opening remark?

94
00:04:12,139 --> 00:04:14,443
By her own admission,

95
00:04:14,445 --> 00:04:17,707
the meta-human known as Killer
Frost is guilty of crimes

96
00:04:17,709 --> 00:04:20,449
that have endangered
the peace of our city

97
00:04:20,451 --> 00:04:22,756
and the safety of our citizens.

98
00:04:22,758 --> 00:04:24,627
And the State finds it absurd that

99
00:04:24,629 --> 00:04:26,673
a former DA would
romanticize this narrative

100
00:04:26,675 --> 00:04:29,458
to avoid punishment.

101
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:32,289
It's early and I haven't
had my coffee, Counselor.

102
00:04:32,292 --> 00:04:33,810
But I don't believe the defendant is

103
00:04:33,812 --> 00:04:35,638
asking to avoid punishment.

104
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,988
Agreed, Your Honor.

105
00:04:37,990 --> 00:04:41,166
But the State has one goal...

106
00:04:41,168 --> 00:04:43,951
To ensure that this
extremely dangerous criminal

107
00:04:43,953 --> 00:04:46,910
no longer threatens our good citizens...

108
00:04:46,912 --> 00:04:49,435
Which is why we believe

109
00:04:49,437 --> 00:04:51,997
she must have her powers erased.

110
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,440
[spectators reacts]

111
00:04:54,442 --> 00:04:57,546
Your Honor, that is highly irregular.

112
00:04:57,549 --> 00:04:59,332
I'll decide that, Ms. Horton.

113
00:04:59,335 --> 00:05:01,055
Ms. Strong, please continue.

114
00:05:01,057 --> 00:05:02,622
In lieu of prison,

115
00:05:02,624 --> 00:05:05,043
the State moves to submit
alternate punishment...

116
00:05:05,046 --> 00:05:09,585
That Killer Frost be
compelled by this court...

117
00:05:09,587 --> 00:05:12,110
