149
00:06:34,642 --> 00:06:37,556
so that I could go and
break the law again.

150
00:06:37,558 --> 00:06:40,460
We're doing this by the book
or not at all... okay, Katie?

151
00:06:43,564 --> 00:06:45,607
Okay. You're right.

152
00:06:45,609 --> 00:06:48,131
Something still doesn't sit right.

153
00:06:48,133 --> 00:06:51,614
Why would Kramer go so
hard to take you down?

154
00:06:51,617 --> 00:06:54,486
I have no idea.

155
00:06:54,488 --> 00:06:56,848
But all I care about
now is stopping her.

156
00:06:56,851 --> 00:06:58,794
Well, we do that by convincing the judge

157
00:06:58,796 --> 00:07:01,493
that you deserve prison
time and not the cure.

158
00:07:01,495 --> 00:07:03,886
I got some case law
books back at the office

159
00:07:03,888 --> 00:07:06,933
that we need to look at, and uh, Joe,

160
00:07:06,935 --> 00:07:10,373
I think you can help me out.

161
00:07:19,034 --> 00:07:20,860
Okay, what are we really doing?

162
00:07:20,862 --> 00:07:23,558
- I like your hacking idea.
- We need to think bigger.

163
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,518
Frost's life is on the line.

164
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,737
Guys, I'm still picking up

165
00:07:28,739 --> 00:07:30,478
Fuerza's isotopic signature in the area.

166
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,784
You still don't see her?

167
00:07:31,786 --> 00:07:33,222
No, nothing yet.

168
00:07:34,789 --> 00:07:38,007
Fuerza's signature is seismic-based.

169
00:07:38,009 --> 00:07:40,664
Maybe she hides underground.

170
00:07:42,449 --> 00:07:44,318
Man, there's a lot of people here.

171
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:47,590
