before things get dangerous.

172
00:07:47,593 --> 00:07:51,238
No. The Forces want to
feed off our powers, Barry.

173
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:53,371
That's probably why
this thing attacked you

174
00:07:53,373 --> 00:07:55,503
in the first place.

175
00:07:55,505 --> 00:07:58,895
