00:08:06,015 --> 00:08:08,429
We know all we need to.

180
00:08:08,431 --> 00:08:10,953
They're dangerous.

181
00:08:10,955 --> 00:08:12,825
I still remember how they attacked me...

182
00:08:12,827 --> 00:08:15,697
Eating me alive.

183
00:08:15,699 --> 00:08:17,132
I could feel it.

184
00:08:17,135 --> 00:08:18,507
