when Psych attacked me.

186
00:08:21,357 --> 00:08:24,358
Wherever these things came
from, they have to be stopped.

187
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,937
Yeah, I'm not so sure.

188
00:08:25,940 --> 00:08:27,496
What do you mean?

189
00:08:27,499 --> 00:08:30,102
Well, the Sage Force
is clearly dangerous

190
00:08:30,105 --> 00:08:31,851
and Fuerza too, but do you remember

191
00:08:31,854 --> 00:08:34,700
what Chester and Cisco said
about Deon, the Still Force?

192
00:08:34,703 --> 00:08:37,101
That he was just a kid who
wanted to be left alone.

193
00:08:37,104 --> 00:08:38,313
Yeah, I mean, does that seem like

194
00:08:38,315 --> 00:08:40,278
a vicious energy feeder to you?

195
00:08:40,281 --> 00:08:42,007
Something doesn't add up here.

196
00:08:42,010 --> 00:08:43,595
Barry, the creature that we're hunting

197
00:08:43,597 --> 00:08:45,528
killed someone and tried to kill you.

198
00:08:45,531 --> 00:08:47,555
We can't let ourselves be fooled by the

199
00:08:47,557 --> 00:08:50,166
human facades these Forces hide behind.

200
00:08:50,168 --> 00:08:53,300
Underneath them, these
Forces only have one goal...

201
00:08:53,302 --> 00:08:55,731
To destroy everything they touch.

202
00:08:55,734 --> 00:08:58,133
You need to remember that.

