Officer Korber, I'm Caitlin Snow.

218
00:09:57,932 --> 00:09:59,671
I was detained here the other day.

219
00:09:59,673 --> 00:10:01,645
- It was a misunderstanding.
- Right, I heard.

220
00:10:01,648 --> 00:10:03,144
- Sorry that happened.
- It's okay.

221
00:10:03,147 --> 00:10:05,719
