00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,915
When we gave them the cure,

238
00:10:43,918 --> 00:10:46,021
they stored the surplus in the Armory.

239
00:10:46,023 --> 00:10:48,284
- That's where you're headed.
- Uh...

